This paper deals with automatic text summarization of student feedback, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). The paper also mentions the use of metrics such as ROUGE, which is commonly used in NLP evaluation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for summarization, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper deals with educational technology and human-computer interaction, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) or cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
